OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud,
OL,6,Fcloud and patchy fog extending
OL,7,Fnorthwards overnight. Many places
OL,8,Fstaying dry, although some isolated
OL,9,Flight rain or drizzle is possible at
OL,10,Ftimes. Rather mild overall and winds
OL,11,Fremaining generally light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FExtensive low cloud and any
OL,14,Fdrizzle slowly lifting, with brighter
OL,15,Fspells possible, especially during the
OL,16,Fafternoon. Mainly dry, although a
OL,17,Fchance of showery rain from late
OL,18,Fafternoon. Feeling milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
